# Gitignore-like rules for obsidian-export-helper.
# Keep this file next to the executable, or in the directory from which you run it.
# Rules are matched against paths inside the Obsidian vault.

# Ignore a folder and everything inside it.
# private/

# Ignore one note by its path inside the vault.
# Notes/secret.md

# Ignore files by extension anywhere in the vault.
# *.psd
# *.tmp

# Ignore markdown notes in one folder.
# drafts/*.md

# Re-include a file that was ignored by an earlier rule.
# !drafts/keep.md
